    "The correlations between SMMCs and targets are indicated by gray lines (B).",
    "Based on the \"holistic concept\" of TCVM, the main etiologies for endometritis are Qi deficiency (NEB), blood stasis, and external evil invasion.",
    "In accordance with TCVM theory, the uterine inflammation that endometritis dairy cows suffer from is typically caused by bacterial infection, a form of external evil invasion, and is usually accompanied by energy deficiency and blood stasis (Dervishi et al., 2021; Lean et al., 2023).",
    "To validate the connection of endometritis with NEB and blood stasis, we performed experiments both on BEECs under NEB condition and on rats with blood stasis.",
    "The results indicate that energy deficiency and blood stasis each can trigger inflammatory factor release, thus verifying the association between Qi deficiency, blood stasis, and external evil invasion."
